{"tid":2050061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧見民運領袖王丹：很榮幸會見中國共產黨殘暴鎮壓下英勇地以民主運動抵抗的勇者","createTime":"2020-06-04T01:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T01:59:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2ddd5c6b264a74301ccfc389f9972cd1d63171","tid":2050061,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"冷戰反共語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de08b05d2a64aa8c82be50e046ce612cf91a1058","tid":2050061,"uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:22:30.000Z","msg":"六四31年！美國務卿見天安門倖存者 王丹獻策對付中共 - 國際 - 自由時報電子報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/04/php5ovP8x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2Fphp5ovP8x.jpg&h=4bafc595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿龐皮歐（右2）2日接見六四事件倖存者李恆青（右1）、李蘭菊（左1）、蘇曉康（左2）、王丹（中）。（圖取自美國國務院臉書）<br />\n<br />\n首次上稿 00:16<br />\n更新時間 01:18<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）3日會見中國1989年天安門事件倖存的學運領袖王丹等人，國務院在北京時間6月4日零時（美東時間3日中午12點）公開會晤照片，王丹還當面獻上3計對付中國。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發布會晤照片中，龐皮歐與六四倖存者李恆青、李蘭菊、蘇曉康、王丹等人合影。國務院發言人歐塔加斯（Morgan Ortagus）表示，龐皮歐很榮幸地會見「中國共產黨殘暴鎮壓下英勇地以民主運動抵抗」的4位勇者，當年有數千人參與抗爭行動。<br />\n<br />\n王丹在臉書指出，龐皮歐表達了對六四事件31週年的關切，並希望了解倖存者們對於美國「應當如何幫助中國走向民主化」的看法。<br />\n<br />\n王丹提到：「我在表達了對國務卿先生會見我們的感謝之後，提出三條建議：一，美國對華政策應當轉向與中國的公民社會和中國人民的直接對話；二，在未來的中美貿易談判中，應當把改善中國勞工的人權狀況，以及解除中國的網絡封鎖兩個議題放進談判清單；三，美國應當幫助中國人民了解包括『六四』在內的很多歷史事件的真相。」<br />\n<br />\n王丹表示，這是30年來美國國務卿首次公開透過正式會面，表達美國政府對六四事件和中國民主化的關切，這是「歷史性的會見」，他強調：「我在此，再次感謝國務卿蓬皮歐先生對中國走向民主的期待與支持。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3186684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3186684&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=fa32d618\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3186684&h=275a5bf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3186684</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/15877306073/posts/10157275249316074/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F15877306073%2Fposts%2F10157275249316074%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=2a5c27fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/15877306073/posts/10157275249316074/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"83815550d60d8e663ae96e37dc6b643ab19344d2","tid":2050061,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"分裂國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那準備派出戰狼"},{"pid":"82ea9d0e5c02849d8ec32a661ecdc9aa28ab73c5","tid":2050061,"uid":37957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"走佬領袖柴玲呢？<br />\n美國唔見佢，係咪認證咗佢已經投共？"},{"pid":"dc1d46d2721665d884d3066bf188d7090d2954c2","tid":2050061,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:30:50.000Z","msg":"獻三計？<br />\n獻三夢咋嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6beb3836ee11af4eb7381cde660e1e195305ca","tid":2050061,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc1d46d2721665d884d3066bf188d7090d2954c2","tid":2050061,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:30:50.000Z","msg":"獻三計？<br />\n獻三夢咋嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re